WEBVTT

41:26.870 --> 41:29.000 line:80%
She came to Lin'an pregnant back then,

41:29.830 --> 41:30.870 line:80%
with no relatives to turn to.

41:30.870 --> 41:32.600 line:80%
She was even worse off than you.

41:32.720 --> 41:33.920 line:80%
Where is her husband?

41:34.470 --> 41:35.600 line:80%
I don't know.

41:35.600 --> 41:36.990 line:80%
He must be capable.
